OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fout to stop suicides       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Universities are being told to contact 
OL,6, key family members, carers or friends  
OL,7, if they have serious concerns about a  
OL,8, student's mental health - even without 
OL,9, their permission.                      
OL,11,FStudents should register a "trusted    
OL,12,Fcontact" when they start university,   
OL,13,Faccording to new guidance.             
OL,15,FUniversities UK (UUK) said its advice, 
OL,16,Fwhich it shared with BBC News, aimed to
OL,17,Fprevent student suicides.              
OL,19,FBereaved loved ones say universities   
OL,20,Fneed to act on their policies.         
